# ============================================================================
# REGISTRATION FLOW CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================
# 
# Configuration for the enhanced registration flow (email + Google OAuth)
# 
# These variables control:
# - Session timeout during registration (30 minutes default)
# - Email verification token expiry (24 hours default)
# - Password hashing security (bcrypt cost factor)
# - API endpoints for registration
# 
# All these variables are already configured above in the appropriate sections.
# 
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# SUMMARY
# ============================================================================
# 
# Minimum required for basic development:
# ✅ NODE_ENV, DEBUG, NEXT_PUBLIC_DEBUG
# 
# Required for full functionality:
# ✅ Google OAuth (login)
# ✅ Supabase (database)
# ✅ Stripe (payments)
# 
# Required for registration flow:
# ✅ JWT_SECRET (OAuth registration)
# ✅ BCRYPT_COST_FACTOR (password hashing)
# ✅ SESSION_TIMEOUT (registration session)
# ✅ VERIFICATION_TOKEN_EXPIRY (email verification)
# ✅ SMTP configuration (email verification)
# 
# Optional but recommended:
# ⚠️ Discord Webhook (notifications)
# ⚠️ Amazon Associates (affiliate links)
# 
# Optional for specific features:
# ⚠️ Monero (crypto payments)
# ⚠️ Database/Redis (if using Docker)
# 
# ============================================================================
